author: gtully
msg: further evolution of resolution for https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/AMQ-2590 - indoubt transactions are now rolledback, pending transactions can wait for jms.consumerFailoverRedeliveryWaitPeriod for redeliveries before rolling back. If previously delivered messages are not replayed the transaction is rolledback
